premise_source_doc_sentence: He has been starring in the drama series Blue Bloods as Danny Reagan with Tom Selleck  (  his TV father  )  and Bridget Moynahan  (  his TV sister  )  since 2010 , and since 2014 is an executive producer of the TNT reality television show Boston 's Finest .
Actors Donnie Wahlberg , Bridget Moynahan , Will Estes , Len Cariou and Tom Selleck round out the main cast as the Reagan family - Danny , Erin , Jamie , Henry and Frank .
